{"tid":1762036,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中國人湧入俄羅斯遠東地區，部分人歡迎，部分人反感","createTime":"2019-11-29T10:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T01:10:15.000Z","uid":133680,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"11d4d1e0d58a54d7010147ec1b2ac177d4d281eb","tid":1762036,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50415886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50415886&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=2ac7e098\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50415886&h=8dd4f386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50415886</a><br />\n<br />\n中國農民湧入俄羅斯遠東？當地人怎樣看這群「新鄰居」<br />\n2019年 11月 15日<br />\n分享平台 微博 分享平台 人人網 分享平台 電郵 分享<br />\n俄羅斯廣袤的遠東地區長期地廣人稀，但近年來不斷湧入的中國人讓這裏熱鬧起來。他們中的大多數人都從事農業工作，儘管部分地區的法律明令禁止移民從事類似活動。<br />\n<br />\n這裏的居民對中國人的看法愛恨交織。俄羅斯科學院2017年的一項調查顯示，超過三分之一的受訪者表示，他們認為中國的對俄政策是「擴張」；但也有人認為，如果中國人離開，這裏將淪為荒地。<br />\n<br />\nBBC俄語記者前往俄羅斯遠東的阿穆爾州、猶太自治州和濱海邊疆區等地，看看那裏的居民們怎樣看他們的「新鄰居」。<br />\n<br />\n影片製作：葉卡捷琳娜&middot;文尼迪科娃（Ekaterina Venediktova）、安德烈&middot;扎哈羅夫（Andrei Zakharov）、瑪麗亞&middot;扎科迪亞琴科（Maria Zakhodiaichenko）"},{"pid":"1f93856b9fed1d4ee3c1cc37b46d6b8fb55fcd38","tid":1762036,"uid":173179,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實唔係侵略<br />\n係狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b66fefed446059e708f5d06720702461ae35f49","tid":1762036,"uid":134774,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"兩大地球毒瘤"},{"pid":"e87e98a78d20b31fd184490781bc72a51c789aba","tid":1762036,"uid":58387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10: